import React from 'react'
import { Modal, Input } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const InputExampleAction = (props) => <Input action='Save' placeholder='Go for a run...'onChange={props.onUpdateInput} />

const ModalExampleTopAligned = (props) => (
  <Modal open={props.showModal} centered={false}>
    <Modal.Header>Edit your TODO</Modal.Header>
    <Modal.Content>
      <InputExampleAction/>
    </Modal.Content>
  </Modal>
)

export default ModalExampleTopAligned
